          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1703063217959-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1703063217959-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>parsnip[s]</strong> and <strong>potato[es]</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped vegetables</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain and leave them to steam dry, reserving the pot for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1703063222361-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1703063222361-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1703063222361-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1703063222361-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1703063222361-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with the <strong>drained lentils</strong>, your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong> and your <strong>ground allspice </strong>(not a fan of allspice? Don't add it all!), give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1703063227049-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1703063227049-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1703063227049-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
