            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1703063227049-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mixture is cooking, dissolve your <strong>Marmite</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[170ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>stock</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> stock </strong>to the pan with your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>,<strong> </strong>mix everything together and cook for 1-2 min or until the stock has been completely absorbed – this is your <strong>haggis spiced veggie loaf mix</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1703063258818-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
