          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1703063258818-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a <strong>loaf tin</strong> (approx. 23x13x7cm) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong> and grease with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 tins!</p><p>Add the <strong>haggis-spiced veggie loaf mix</strong> to the prepared tin[s], pressing down into the corners and smoothing out the top, then reserve the pan and wipe clean with kitchen paper</p><p>Put in the oven and cook for 20-25 min or until crisp on the top</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1703063285729-x200.jpg",
