          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1703063303987-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Gently turn the <strong>haggis-spiced veggie loaf</strong> out onto a chopping board, let it cool slightly and slice thickly (it's meant to be crumbly!)</p><p>Serve the <strong>haggis-spiced veggie loaf</strong> with the<strong> parsnip mash </strong>and<strong> cavolo nero </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>onion gravy</strong>, dollop your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> to the side and season to taste</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
